About Web Pigeon

Welcome to Web Pigeon, the cutting-edge anonymous web messaging platform that's taking the internet by storm! Our mission is to provide a free, open, and self-regulating communication space for everyone.

What makes Web Pigeon unique?

  • Fully public messengers - transparency at its finest
  • No encryption - because true anonymity starts with you
  • Self-regulating community - power to the users
  • Retro-inspired design - nostalgia meets functionality

Web Pigeon is more than just a proof of concept - it's a fully functional, scalable solution ready to revolutionize online communication. Our Windows 98-inspired interface brings a touch of nostalgia while delivering cutting-edge functionality.

Remember: With great anonymity comes great responsibility. Use Web Pigeon wisely and respect your fellow pigeons!
